				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Kiting works excellently for bards as well, up to and including red creatures. If you can hit it with your Bellow, you CAN kill it, no matter how it cons to you. The trick is twisting- have Selo's Accelerando up when you find your victim, then bellow to get their attention. You can, with proper timing, get off 2 bellows and switch back to Selo's before it's effect wears off. Then it's just round and round, until the beast drops dead.
